# Guess My Number

Project was done as part of The complete JavaScript Course with Udemy.

Useful features learnt:
- [x] DOM Manipulation
- [x] Selecting and manipulating HTMl elements using querySelector
- [x] Manipulating CSS styles
- [x] Handling click events using addEventListener
- [x] Implementing Game Logic using detailed if else statements
- [x] Implementing highscores (keeping track of user performance even after restoring functionalities)
- [x] Understanding input fields
- [x] Refactoring code with DRY Principle in mind
